Security controls are safeguards that reduce security risks. Common types used in the Cloud include:

| Control Type | Description (EN) | DescriÃ§Ã£o (PT) | Practical Example |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **ğŸ†” Identity** | Authenticates a user before they access resources. | Autentica um usuÃ¡rio antes de acessar recursos. | Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA). |
| **ğŸ›¡ï¸ Protective** | Shields against malicious attacks and protects access. | Protege contra ataques maliciosos e blinda o acesso. | Antivirus, WAF, IaC policies. |
| **ğŸŒ Network** | Protects access through network paths (firewalls). | Protege o acesso atravÃ©s de caminhos de rede. | Cloud Firewalls / VPC Firewalls. |
| **ğŸ” Detective** | Identifies suspicious activity if it occurs. | Identifica atividades suspeitas caso ocorram. | Intrusion Detection Systems (IDS). |
| **ğŸ¤– Responsive** | Uses automation to respond to security events. | Usa automaÃ§Ã£o para responder a eventos de seguranÃ§a. | Automated alert emails / Auto-quarantine. |
| **ğŸ”„ Recovery** | Restores access/functionality in the event of failures. | Restaura acesso/funcionalidade em caso de falhas. | Backups and System Restoration. |

